NOTIFICATION SYSTEM
@author Farhana Basrawala
@version 1.0

This is a small script that allow you to quickly and simply create alerts.

Usage:

First include the alerts.js file included in the js/lib/alerts folder then follow the example below.

* var NS = new Alerts("#alerts-display-wrap");
* NS.sendAlert('An error has occurred. Please try again', 'error');
